# Handle outliers
handle_outlier_z <- function(col){
  col_z <- scale(col)
  ifelse(abs(col_z)>3,
         sign(col_z)*3*attr(col_z,\scaled:scale\) + attr(col_z,\scaled:center\), col)
}
basetable_train[, num.cols] <-  sapply(basetable_train[, num.cols], FUN = handle_outlier_z)
